# Prism frontend — example environment variables.
# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and adjust. Only `VITE_*` keys are exposed to the
# browser bundle by Vite, so NEVER put secrets (API keys, tokens, connection strings) here.

# CopilotKit Node runtime sidecar URL (package 07).
#   - Dev: leave unset to use the Vite dev-server proxy at `/copilotkit` → http://localhost:4000
#   - Prod: set to the deployed sidecar origin, e.g. https://prism-copilot.example.com/copilotkit
# VITE_COPILOT_URL=/copilotkit
